data.description: Welcome to this expansive 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom Reverse 1.5 Story residence, designed to cater to all your needs and elevate your entertaining experience, be it hosting gatherings or enjoying quality family time. The primary bedroom boasts a private deck, offering an ideal spot to savor your morning coffee. Further enhancing your outdoor lifestyle is a spacious deck and patio, seamlessly blending indoor and outdoor spaces for unforgettable entertainment moments. The walkout basement adds a new dimension to your game days, featuring a complete wet bar/kitchenette and a generously sized family room, ready to accommodate all your friends. Don't miss the opportunity to explore all that this exceptional home has in store for you.
